  "title": "Audit Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>· Provide statutory audit services and compilation of financial statements to clients in various industries</p>\n<p>· Perform audit procedures and related work with guidance and supervision from seniors and managers/partners</p>\n<p>· Other audit and assurance related duties and functions as assigned</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Candidates must be suitably qualified with a Degree or professional qualifications recognized by ISCA.</p>\n<p>· Candidates whom possess a recognized diploma and are currently pursuing a Degree or professional qualifications recognized by ISCA will also be considered.</p>\n<p>· Candidates accompanied by suitable working experience will be considered for senior entry level.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p>\n<p>· The Firm recognizes and acknowledges that the quality of our people are the key drivers to the Firm success and hence, the Firm is constantly on the look-out for dedicated and committed professionals to grow with the Firm.</p>\n<p>· In attracting, retaining and motivating our people the Firm endeavor in providing a continuous learning environment in equipping our people with the necessary skills that help the Firm in fully developing our people potentials and professional growth.</p>\n<p>If you have what it takes:-</p>\n<p>Please email/send your comprehensive resume, including a recent photograph and to include the following details:-</p>\n<p>1. Reasons for leaving current employment</p>\n<p>2. Availability / Notice period required</p>\n<p>3. Last drawn/ current and expected salary</p>\n<p>4. References (if any)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>The Recruitment Partner</strong></p>\n<p><strong>ACFOSS PAC</strong></p>\n<p>100D Pasir Panjang Road #02-11</p>\n<p>Meissa</p>\n<p>Singapore 118520</p>\n<p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:hr@acfoss.com.sg\"><strong>hr@acfoss.com.sg</strong></a></p>\n<p>Website : www.acfoss.com.sg</p>\n<p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em></p>",
